OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan held after 'terrifying 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhostage ordeal' at hotel   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A person was taken hostage by a man    
OL,6, armed with what was believed to have   
OL,7, been a gun in a Belfast hotel.         
OL,9,FPolice were told that a man with a gun 
OL,10,Fwas in the Clayton Hotel on Sunday     
OL,11,Fevening, threatening staff and guests. 
OL,13,FThe police said officers were on the   
OL,14,Fscene within minutes and when they     
OL,15,Farrived, a man had been taken hostage. 
OL,17,FSpecially-trained officers arrived     
OL,18,Fshortly afterwards and the hostage was 
OL,19,Freleased. A 31-year-old man was later  
OL,20,Farrested.                              
